field.value:
It would be nice to have the WcfFacility be able to register all the interfaces inside an assembly.
i.e)
{code lang=java}
AllTypes.FromAssemblyContaining<IBusinessFunctionDAO>()
                    .Where(o => o.Name.EndsWith("DAO"))
                    .Configure(
                        o => o.AsWcfClient(WcfEndpoint.FromConfiguration("WSHttpBinding_" + o.Name))
                    )
{code}
This would help out when you have a lot of ServiceContracts in an assembly.
